WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 30=

00:01:38.540 --> 00:01:39.460 line:80%
Young Master,

00:01:39.460 --> 00:01:40.300 line:80%
this time,

00:01:40.540 --> 00:01:43.180 line:80%
Miss Cai took seven lashes
of the Python Whip.

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:45.370 line:80%
Though her life is not in danger,

00:01:45.780 --> 00:01:46.930 line:80%
such wounds

00:01:47.290 --> 00:01:48.650 line:80%
require time to heal.

00:01:49.540 --> 00:01:51.540 line:80%
Lord Qi has also placed Miss Cai
under confinement

00:01:51.540 --> 00:01:55.010 line:80%
in the Realm Cavern
of Thousandfold Cliff,

00:01:55.700 --> 00:01:57.340 line:80%
punishing her to reflect for a year.

00:01:58.820 --> 00:01:59.850 line:80%
During this year,

00:02:00.780 --> 00:02:02.060 line:80%
only Song Yuzhi

00:02:02.370 --> 00:02:03.490 line:80%
may enter and leave

00:02:03.780 --> 00:02:04.700 line:80%
to look after her.

00:02:06.650 --> 00:02:07.650 line:80%
If it's him,

00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:11.460 line:80%
he'll surely care for her
with utmost devotion.

00:02:11.930 --> 00:02:12.970 line:80%
Young Master,

00:02:13.230 --> 00:02:14.090 line:80%
you and Miss Cai...

00:02:14.090 --> 00:02:15.140 line:80%
From now on,

00:02:15.810 --> 00:02:16.790 line:80%
we go our separate ways.

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:19.740 line:80%
From this day forward,

00:02:19.740 --> 00:02:21.900 line:80%
no one in the sect is
to speak of her again.

00:02:28.090 --> 00:02:28.930 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:41.300 --> 00:02:42.140 line:80%
Take

00:02:42.810 --> 00:02:43.650 line:80%
this luminous pearl.

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:45.199 line:80%
You're afraid of the dark.

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:46.780 line:80%
With it,

00:02:47.490 --> 00:02:50.740 line:80%
you can at least sleep peacefully.

00:03:27.970 --> 00:03:28.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:03:29.970 --> 00:03:30.810 line:80%
it's time to eat.

00:03:31.180 --> 00:03:33.180 line:80%
Yuzhi, you're early today.

00:03:33.530 --> 00:03:34.780 line:80%
I'm not hungry yet.

00:03:35.580 --> 00:03:36.420 line:80%
It's back to you.

00:03:46.060 --> 00:03:46.900 line:80%
True.

00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:48.970 line:80%
What if I run out of money again?

00:03:55.020 --> 00:03:57.140 line:80%
The Python Whip wounds
will only heal slowly.

00:03:57.690 --> 00:03:59.090 line:80%
Zhao, you must be careful as well.

00:03:59.810 --> 00:04:00.690 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:03.410 line:80%
As long as I don't move,
it doesn't hurt.

00:04:05.410 --> 00:04:06.490 line:80%
This was sent by Lord Zhou.

00:04:06.490 --> 00:04:07.970 line:80%
It relieves pain and promotes healing.

00:04:10.340 --> 00:04:12.210 line:80%
I injured Uncle Zhou before.

00:04:13.530 --> 00:04:14.970 line:80%
Yet he still worries about me.

00:04:15.460 --> 00:04:17.090 line:80%
Lord Zhou knows you didn't mean it.

00:04:17.380 --> 00:04:18.610 line:80%
He said his injuries are

00:04:19.020 --> 00:04:19.860 line:80%
nothing serious.

00:04:21.730 --> 00:04:23.380 line:80%
Uncle Zhou wants to ask

00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:26.340 line:80%
about Aunt and Mu Zhengyang, right?

00:04:28.850 --> 00:04:30.530 line:80%
Aunt did once care for Mu Zhengyang.

00:04:31.210 --> 00:04:32.380 line:80%
But after his death,

00:04:34.020 --> 00:04:34.860 line:80%
she never

00:04:35.970 --> 00:04:37.940 line:80%
spoke another word of it.

00:04:39.050 --> 00:04:41.050 line:80%
She must've let it go.

00:04:41.730 --> 00:04:43.210 line:80%
There is nothing more to say.

00:04:44.500 --> 00:04:46.410 line:80%
Her longing faded just like that.

00:04:48.020 --> 00:04:49.500 line:80%
Ms. Cai was carefree,

00:04:49.850 --> 00:04:50.690 line:80%
but

00:04:51.140 --> 00:04:51.980 line:80%
their paths diverged,

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:54.140 line:80%
so it was a fleeting dream.

00:04:57.610 --> 00:04:58.450 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:04:58.700 --> 00:05:00.140 line:80%
next time you visit,

00:05:00.530 --> 00:05:02.780 line:80%
bring me some paper and ink.

00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:04.570 line:80%
Sure.

00:05:05.090 --> 00:05:07.210 line:80%
Why suddenly decide to leave?

00:05:10.410 --> 00:05:12.050 line:80%
I've thought about it for a long time.

00:05:14.340 --> 00:05:15.970 line:80%
I used to be immature.

00:05:17.020 --> 00:05:17.900 line:80%
From now on,

00:05:19.050 --> 00:05:21.410 line:80%
I want to become a daughter
whom you're proud of.

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:25.730 line:80%
I never understood before

00:05:26.380 --> 00:05:28.580 line:80%
why you cared more
for the people of Luoying Valley

00:05:28.580 --> 00:05:29.820 line:80%
than for me.

00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:32.146 line:80%
Was it because my martial arts
were poor,

00:05:33.050 --> 00:05:34.050 line:80%
or because

00:05:35.170 --> 00:05:36.580 line:80%
you didn't care for Mother?

00:05:39.700 --> 00:05:40.970 line:80%
But now, I understand.

00:05:41.500 --> 00:05:43.140 line:80%
As leader of the Six Sects,

00:05:43.850 --> 00:05:45.376 line:80%
you must place the greater good first.

00:05:45.460 --> 00:05:46.730 line:80%
You can't focus only on family.

00:05:47.340 --> 00:05:49.146 line:80%
Ms. Cai sacrificed herself
for the Six Sects.

00:05:49.900 --> 00:05:51.580 line:80%
If you didn't care for her family,

00:05:51.580 --> 00:05:53.340 line:80%
wouldn't that chill the hearts of all?

00:05:53.730 --> 00:05:55.530 line:80%
As your daughter,

00:05:57.170 --> 00:05:58.780 line:80%
I should ease his burdens.

00:05:59.170 --> 00:06:00.970 line:80%
Yet instead, I grew jealous

00:06:01.340 --> 00:06:02.180 line:80%
and caused trouble.

00:06:02.900 --> 00:06:04.090 line:80%
I was truly wrong.

00:06:07.410 --> 00:06:08.500 line:80%
All these years,

00:06:08.500 --> 00:06:10.530 line:80%
I've indeed neglected you.

00:06:12.500 --> 00:06:13.650 line:80%
In my heart,

00:06:14.820 --> 00:06:16.090 line:80%
I feel guilt.

00:06:21.020 --> 00:06:22.900 line:80%
It's my problem.

00:06:28.530 --> 00:06:30.610 line:80%
(Pillar of Jianghu)
I know my aptitude is poor.

00:06:31.020 --> 00:06:33.050 line:80%
It's hard for me to achieve much
in martial arts.

00:06:33.380 --> 00:06:34.940 line:80%
But as a member of the Six Sects,

00:06:34.940 --> 00:06:36.610 line:80%
I can't hide on this mountain

00:06:36.970 --> 00:06:38.140 line:80%
just because I can't fight.

00:06:38.820 --> 00:06:39.820 line:80%
This time,

00:06:40.940 --> 00:06:42.610 line:80%
I wish to follow Ms. Cai's example,

00:06:43.050 --> 00:06:43.970 line:80%
uphold justice,

00:06:44.850 --> 00:06:46.183 line:80%
and bring glory to the Six Sects.

00:06:47.850 --> 00:06:50.850 line:80%
I don't wish you to become like Ms. Cai.

00:06:51.210 --> 00:06:52.380 line:80%
Jianghu is dangerous.

00:06:52.970 --> 00:06:54.090 line:80%
I only hope

00:06:54.090 --> 00:06:56.290 line:80%
you can live this life in peace and joy

00:06:57.290 --> 00:06:59.340 line:80%
by my side.

00:07:08.340 --> 00:07:10.580 line:80%
So, you do care for me.

00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:13.610 line:80%
Then I must not remain weak and useless.

00:07:18.650 --> 00:07:21.020 line:80%
Ever since Zhao was confined,

00:07:21.020 --> 00:07:23.170 line:80%
Qingque Sect hasn't been as lively.

00:07:25.140 --> 00:07:25.980 line:80%
Is she any better?

00:07:26.290 --> 00:07:27.580 line:80%
Seven lashes of the Python Whip.

00:07:28.020 --> 00:07:29.290 line:80%
Injuries to sinew and bone

00:07:29.290 --> 00:07:30.460 line:80%
don't heal so quickly.

00:07:30.460 --> 00:07:31.900 line:80%
It's good enough that she's awakened.

00:07:33.276 --> 00:07:35.309 line:80%
We just sold the first batch
of golden silk armor.

00:07:35.460 --> 00:07:37.650 line:80%
These insect repellent samples
must be sent down asap.

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:40.380 line:80%
There's still much unfinished business
waiting for Zhao.

00:07:40.380 --> 00:07:41.220 line:80%
Enough.

00:07:42.210 --> 00:07:44.460 line:80%
We haven't even practiced,
yet we are all helping you.

00:07:44.460 --> 00:07:45.746 line:80%
And you keep talking about Zhao.

00:07:45.757 --> 00:07:47.140 line:80%
Enough of that. Let's go.

00:07:47.140 --> 00:07:47.980 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:07:48.820 --> 00:07:50.046 line:80%
Fan is doing this for everyone.

00:07:50.340 --> 00:07:52.020 line:80%
Master donated the money
left by Lord Yin

00:07:52.020 --> 00:07:52.860 line:80%
to Jiangdong

00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:55.093 line:80%
and waived the fees for outer disciples.

00:07:55.500 --> 00:07:57.170 line:80%
If not for Fan managing things,

00:07:57.170 --> 00:07:58.340 line:80%
the sect wouldn't be running.

00:07:58.960 --> 00:07:59.850 line:80%
Just doing my duty.

00:07:59.850 --> 00:08:00.690 line:80%
My duty.

00:08:01.850 --> 00:08:03.780 line:80%
If Zhao hadn't been confined,

00:08:03.780 --> 00:08:05.700 line:80%
we wouldn't be so short of funds.

00:08:05.700 --> 00:08:07.460 line:80%
She's clever and full of ideas.

00:08:07.460 --> 00:08:08.940 line:80%
You've mentioned her confinement

00:08:08.940 --> 00:08:10.430 line:80%
countless times today.

00:08:10.430 --> 00:08:11.280 line:80%
With that time,

00:08:11.290 --> 00:08:12.900 line:80%
you might as well send the samples down.

00:08:16.500 --> 00:08:17.340 line:80%
I'll go.

00:08:19.210 --> 00:08:20.170 line:80%
After years of study,

00:08:20.530 --> 00:08:22.140 line:80%
it's time to gain experience.

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:24.610 line:80%
You truly plan to go down?

00:08:25.500 --> 00:08:26.340 line:80%
Then be careful.

00:08:26.340 --> 00:08:27.793 line:80%
Help me open a few new trade routes.

00:08:29.340 --> 00:08:30.780 line:80%
Fengchi, you...

00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:32.940 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:08:33.380 --> 00:08:34.326 line:80%
I've thought it through.

00:08:35.100 --> 00:08:36.530 line:80%
Only by aiming high

00:08:36.530 --> 00:08:37.370 line:80%
and becoming capable

00:08:37.930 --> 00:08:39.650 line:80%
can I stand by your side to protect you

00:08:40.220 --> 00:08:41.220 line:80%
and keep you safe.

00:09:00.380 --> 00:09:01.290 line:80%
This is Hui's paper.

00:09:01.860 --> 00:09:03.100 line:80%
The ink will last longer.

00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:04.740 line:80%
If it's not enough, tell me.

00:09:05.140 --> 00:09:06.050 line:80%
I'll buy more.

00:09:07.050 --> 00:09:09.530 line:80%
You bring paper every three days.

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:12.170 line:80%
This is enough to last for two years.

00:09:14.100 --> 00:09:15.930 line:80%
If sect affairs are busy,

00:09:15.930 --> 00:09:18.530 line:80%
you need not come so often.

00:09:19.930 --> 00:09:20.770 line:80%
It's no trouble.

00:09:48.900 --> 00:09:50.500 line:80%
Master has confined me for a year.

00:09:51.020 --> 00:09:52.740 line:80%
Though it seems harsh and heartless,

00:09:53.330 --> 00:09:54.330 line:80%
I know

00:09:54.780 --> 00:09:56.410 line:80%
he is calming the storm for me.

00:09:58.100 --> 00:09:59.050 line:80%
During this time,

00:09:59.780 --> 00:10:01.740 line:80%
I can write down

00:10:01.740 --> 00:10:02.686 line:80%
my thoughts and records.

00:10:03.570 --> 00:10:05.050 line:80%
When I emerge next year,

00:10:05.930 --> 00:10:07.020 line:80%
I'll be a heroine once more.

00:10:09.220 --> 00:10:11.170 line:80%
Master always praises you
for your quick mind.

00:10:12.050 --> 00:10:13.620 line:80%
You truly understand his intentions.

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:15.820 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:10:16.330 --> 00:10:18.500 line:80%
do you know what kind of storybook
I intend to write?

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:22.500 line:80%
You must want to write about Miss Cai,

00:10:22.810 --> 00:10:23.780 line:80%
Uncle Guo,

00:10:24.570 --> 00:10:27.140 line:80%
and my grandfather.

00:10:27.780 --> 00:10:29.020 line:80%
As for Lord Yin,

00:10:30.860 --> 00:10:32.530 line:80%
I won't write any flattering words.

00:10:32.810 --> 00:10:33.780 line:80%
If it's true,

00:10:34.330 --> 00:10:35.170 line:80%
why not?

00:10:37.620 --> 00:10:38.570 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:40.180 line:80%
you're a true gentleman.

00:10:45.140 --> 00:10:46.620 line:80%
A few days ago, Lingbo sent word back.

00:10:47.140 --> 00:10:47.980 line:80%
In her letter,

00:10:48.330 --> 00:10:50.256 line:80%
she wrote of all she saw and heard
with Fengchi.

00:10:50.860 --> 00:10:52.330 line:80%
It sounded carefree and delightful.

00:10:54.170 --> 00:10:55.530 line:80%
Lingbo has finally

00:10:55.980 --> 00:10:57.810 line:80%
faced her heart.

00:11:01.810 --> 00:11:03.930 line:80%
Yuzhi, do you know why I wish to leave?

00:11:06.330 --> 00:11:07.570 line:80%
Because I dislike Cai Zhao.

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:11.290 line:80%
I dislike that she cares about nothing.

00:11:12.530 --> 00:11:14.570 line:80%
I dislike that she took
your and Father's favor.

00:11:15.140 --> 00:11:16.740 line:80%
I dislike that however I bullied her,

00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:18.410 line:80%
she never took it to heart.

00:11:19.290 --> 00:11:21.740 line:80%
I also dislike
that she could go alone for medicine.

00:11:23.570 --> 00:11:25.140 line:80%
I dislike that she saw at a glance

00:11:25.140 --> 00:11:26.020 line:80%
that Father was fake.

00:11:26.980 --> 00:11:29.690 line:80%
I dislike that knowing Mu Qingyan
is the Chief of the demonic sect,

00:11:30.450 --> 00:11:32.330 line:80%
she still saved him without hesitation.

00:11:32.740 --> 00:11:34.410 line:80%
How can she be like that?

00:11:35.900 --> 00:11:37.860 line:80%
How can she be so unrestrained

00:11:37.860 --> 00:11:39.020 line:80%
and free?

00:11:41.810 --> 00:11:42.690 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:11:44.190 --> 00:11:45.620 line:80%
you needn't compare yourself to her.

00:11:45.620 --> 00:11:46.460 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:11:48.980 --> 00:11:50.053 line:80%
I didn't understand before.

00:11:50.740 --> 00:11:52.860 line:80%
But now I do.

00:11:54.650 --> 00:11:55.810 line:80%
I don't dislike her.

00:11:56.740 --> 00:11:57.780 line:80%
I envy her.

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.140 line:80%
The world is vast.

00:12:02.170 --> 00:12:03.740 line:80%
One should live more freely.

00:12:04.410 --> 00:12:05.250 line:80%
So,

00:12:06.220 --> 00:12:07.690 line:80%
I'll do whatever I wish to do.

00:12:14.620 --> 00:12:15.530 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:12:17.810 --> 00:12:19.900 line:80%
you are too calm and restrained.

00:12:20.380 --> 00:12:22.530 line:80%
That's why you are overshadowed
by Mu Qingyan.

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:24.170 line:80%
In this life,

00:12:24.650 --> 00:12:25.980 line:80%
one should live for oneself.

00:12:28.220 --> 00:12:29.220 line:80%
The world is vast.

00:12:30.290 --> 00:12:31.530 line:80%
Live by your heart.

00:12:52.220 --> 00:12:53.450 line:80%
(The world is vast.)

00:12:55.050 --> 00:12:56.530 line:80%
(Live by your heart.)

00:12:57.860 --> 00:12:59.020 line:80%
Lingbo's story

00:12:59.620 --> 00:13:01.290 line:80%
can become another storybook.

00:13:02.780 --> 00:13:03.740 line:80%
Lingbo's courage

00:13:04.650 --> 00:13:06.330 line:80%
has made Fengchi courageous too.

00:13:08.530 --> 00:13:09.980 line:80%
If only one person is brave,

00:13:10.410 --> 00:13:11.570 line:80%
it's likely useless.

00:13:36.530 --> 00:13:38.100 line:80%
Thank you for saving my life.

00:13:40.290 --> 00:13:41.130 line:80%
Sit.

00:13:45.380 --> 00:13:46.650 line:80%
Why did Yu Hui want to kill you?

00:14:04.740 --> 00:14:05.580 line:80%
Fengge,

00:14:06.050 --> 00:14:07.650 line:80%
it was thanks to you again.

00:14:07.900 --> 00:14:09.050 line:80%
You killed the Chief.

00:14:09.740 --> 00:14:11.140 line:80%
His followers won't spare you.

00:14:12.410 --> 00:14:13.450 line:80%
What are your plans?

00:14:13.930 --> 00:14:15.930 line:80%
Once I find the one behind Nie Zhe,

00:14:16.650 --> 00:14:18.530 line:80%
Li Sect is nothing to fear.

00:14:19.810 --> 00:14:21.290 line:80%
Nie Zhe reached this point

00:14:21.780 --> 00:14:22.620 line:80%
because of him.

00:14:22.900 --> 00:14:23.780 line:80%
He manipulated Nie

00:14:24.290 --> 00:14:25.223 line:80%
to refine corpse slaves

00:14:25.380 --> 00:14:26.500 line:80%
and provoke the Six Sects.

00:14:27.170 --> 00:14:28.010 line:80%
Yu,

00:14:29.050 --> 00:14:30.450 line:80%
you must not follow Nie Zhe's path.

00:14:33.410 --> 00:14:34.250 line:80%
Fengge,

00:14:34.780 --> 00:14:35.650 line:80%
I'm hungry.

00:14:36.170 --> 00:14:37.170 line:80%
Find some food.

00:14:49.170 --> 00:14:51.140 line:80%
When I returned with food,

00:14:52.290 --> 00:14:54.330 line:80%
someone else was inside.

00:14:54.780 --> 00:14:56.530 line:80%
As long as you help me kill Mu Qingyan

00:14:56.530 --> 00:14:57.740 line:80%
and avenge them,

00:14:57.740 --> 00:14:58.900 line:80%
I'll do anything.

00:15:00.740 --> 00:15:01.580 line:80%
Who is there?

00:15:09.930 --> 00:15:11.380 line:80%
You know what to do.

00:15:12.450 --> 00:15:13.290 line:80%
Yu.

00:15:17.570 --> 00:15:18.410 line:80%
You...

00:15:23.980 --> 00:15:25.020 line:80%
why?

00:15:25.570 --> 00:15:26.690 line:80%
The Demonic Camp

00:15:26.690 --> 00:15:27.650 line:80%
is gone.

00:15:28.500 --> 00:15:29.740 line:80%
You are of no use to me now.

00:15:35.620 --> 00:15:36.460 line:80%
Fengge,

00:15:37.740 --> 00:15:39.020 line:80%
I'll remember you.

00:15:53.930 --> 00:15:54.980 line:80%
He didn't know

00:15:55.780 --> 00:15:57.740 line:80%
my heart is distinctive.

00:15:59.220 --> 00:16:00.650 line:80%
It's on the other side.

00:16:02.050 --> 00:16:03.690 line:80%
This stab can't take my life.

00:16:05.380 --> 00:16:07.020 line:80%
Master once told me

00:16:08.290 --> 00:16:10.140 line:80%
that however much you like someone,

00:16:10.570 --> 00:16:11.780 line:80%
some secrets

00:16:12.410 --> 00:16:13.900 line:80%
must never be revealed.

00:16:16.290 --> 00:16:17.380 line:80%
I didn't expect

00:16:18.650 --> 00:16:20.290 line:80%
those words to save me.

00:16:21.410 --> 00:16:23.050 line:80%
Did you see the man in black's face?

00:16:23.260 --> 00:16:24.100 line:80%
He wore a mask.

00:16:24.100 --> 00:16:24.940 line:80%
His voice was deep.

00:16:25.650 --> 00:16:27.810 line:80%
His martial arts were unfathomable.

00:16:28.410 --> 00:16:29.780 line:80%
What he seeks

00:16:30.330 --> 00:16:31.620 line:80%
is far more than Li Sect.

00:16:38.930 --> 00:16:40.740 line:80%
Before, I was used by schemers,

00:16:40.740 --> 00:16:41.650 line:80%
aiding evil.

00:16:42.170 --> 00:16:43.290 line:80%
I nearly let Li Sect

00:16:43.290 --> 00:16:44.810 line:80%
fall into the villains' hands.

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:46.710 line:80%
I have shamed Master's teachings.

00:16:47.450 --> 00:16:48.620 line:80%
From this day forth,

00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:50.810 line:80%
I pledge loyalty to you,

00:16:51.900 --> 00:16:52.740 line:80%
to protect Li Sect

00:16:53.330 --> 00:16:54.450 line:80%
and avenge myself.

00:16:58.330 --> 00:16:59.170 line:80%
Rise.

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:17.890 line:80%
Pay closer attention
to those around you.

00:17:18.370 --> 00:17:19.210 line:80%
I believe

00:17:19.810 --> 00:17:21.460 line:80%
that without the Sevens Pill,

00:17:22.290 --> 00:17:24.180 line:80%
your subordinates wouldn't betray you.

00:17:25.980 --> 00:17:27.330 line:80%
Without testing,

00:17:28.530 --> 00:17:29.780 line:80%
you can still have

00:17:30.370 --> 00:17:32.130 line:80%
subordinates loyal to you.

00:17:37.130 --> 00:17:37.970 line:80%
Young Master.

00:17:47.290 --> 00:17:48.180 line:80%
I trust you.

00:18:27.290 --> 00:18:28.810 line:80%
(Without the Jade Sunflower,)

00:18:28.810 --> 00:18:30.740 line:80%
(no progress in the Ziwei Method.)

00:18:32.660 --> 00:18:35.290 line:80%
He retrieved the saliva with my aunt

00:18:35.740 --> 00:18:37.330 line:80%
and knew about the Jade Sunflower.

00:18:38.980 --> 00:18:41.330 line:80%
He approached her with ulterior motives.

00:18:42.980 --> 00:18:45.330 line:80%
(Did Mu Zhengyang practice
the Ziwei Method as well?)

00:19:00.180 --> 00:19:01.890 line:80%
The wedding begins.

00:19:02.460 --> 00:19:03.780 line:80%
Congratulations!

00:19:03.780 --> 00:19:06.700 line:80%
Lay the carpets!

00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:23.810 line:80%
Love begins prosperously!

00:19:26.370 --> 00:19:28.850 line:80%
May you live in harmony

00:19:29.500 --> 00:19:32.460 line:80%
and share old age together!

00:19:34.090 --> 00:19:34.980 line:80%
Congratulations!

00:19:40.890 --> 00:19:44.290 line:80%
The newlyweds kneel.

00:19:46.610 --> 00:19:48.180 line:80%
First bow.

00:19:52.850 --> 00:19:54.460 line:80%
Second bow.

00:19:56.570 --> 00:19:57.980 line:80%
Third bow.

00:19:58.420 --> 00:19:59.610 line:80%
Rise.

00:20:03.500 --> 00:20:05.780 line:80%
The couple bows to each other.

00:20:12.090 --> 00:20:14.180 line:80%
Thank the Young Master.

00:20:31.530 --> 00:20:32.370 line:80%
A gift.

00:20:34.660 --> 00:20:35.660 line:80%
Thanks, Young Master.

00:20:35.850 --> 00:20:36.690 line:80%
Young Master,

00:20:37.020 --> 00:20:38.810 line:80%
you gave Master You such a grand gift.

00:20:39.610 --> 00:20:40.850 line:80%
When I married...

00:20:40.850 --> 00:20:41.810 line:80%
Come on.

00:20:41.810 --> 00:20:42.850 line:80%
You've married twice.

00:20:42.850 --> 00:20:45.330 line:80%
Do you expect the Young Master
to send two gifts?

00:20:46.370 --> 00:20:47.740 line:80%
Honey.

00:20:50.130 --> 00:20:51.220 line:80%
The ceremony is complete.

00:20:54.180 --> 00:20:56.370 line:80%
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

00:21:19.420 --> 00:21:20.890 line:80%
Smiley.

00:21:20.890 --> 00:21:22.850 line:80%
How did you know I wanted to eat Smiley?

00:21:23.090 --> 00:21:24.780 line:80%
It was sent from the Hanhai Mountains.

00:21:25.330 --> 00:21:26.876 line:80%
I heard they've been holding a wedding.

00:21:29.530 --> 00:21:30.530 line:80%
A wedding?

00:21:31.130 --> 00:21:33.180 line:80%
Master You insisted I deliver it to you.

00:21:33.570 --> 00:21:34.940 line:80%
Xing did us a favor after all.

00:21:35.530 --> 00:21:36.903 line:80%
We can't refuse her wedding sweets.

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:40.220 line:80%
So, it's You Guanyue and Xing's wedding.

00:21:43.850 --> 00:21:44.690 line:80%
So sweet.

00:21:51.850 --> 00:21:52.690 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:56.180 --> 00:21:57.500 line:80%
- I...
- Yuzhi,

00:21:58.850 --> 00:22:00.090 line:80%
my ink is almost gone.

00:22:05.570 --> 00:22:06.410 line:80%
I...

00:22:07.570 --> 00:22:08.740 line:80%
I'll buy you more.

00:22:09.330 --> 00:22:10.850 line:80%
Then thank you, Yuzhi.

00:22:11.610 --> 00:22:12.780 line:80%
I've thought it through.

00:22:13.330 --> 00:22:14.940 line:80%
From this round of bookshop earnings,

00:22:15.980 --> 00:22:17.290 line:80%
I'll give you 20%.

00:22:23.570 --> 00:22:24.876 line:80%
Then you should focus on writing.

00:22:25.810 --> 00:22:26.650 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:22:27.890 --> 00:22:28.810 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:22:46.700 --> 00:22:48.610 line:80%
You want to ask about Zhengyang?

00:22:50.530 --> 00:22:51.370 line:80%
After that,

00:22:51.570 --> 00:22:53.130 line:80%
we only met that one time.

00:22:53.530 --> 00:22:54.500 line:80%
That night,

00:22:54.740 --> 00:22:56.610 line:80%
Zhengyang kept speaking of Pingshu,

00:22:57.530 --> 00:22:58.980 line:80%
who was Ms. Cai.

00:22:59.500 --> 00:23:01.530 line:80%
He said Ms. Cai was so good.

00:23:01.780 --> 00:23:03.980 line:80%
He was truly happy that night,

00:23:03.980 --> 00:23:06.570 line:80%
saying we'd live good days ahead,

00:23:06.570 --> 00:23:07.570 line:80%
and told me to take care.

00:23:07.570 --> 00:23:08.940 line:80%
Take care of what?

00:23:08.940 --> 00:23:10.135 line:80%
He was the one who should stop

00:23:10.146 --> 00:23:12.212 line:80%
risking his life in places
like the snow mountains.

00:23:12.780 --> 00:23:14.130 line:80%
Other than the snow mountains,

00:23:14.130 --> 00:23:15.370 line:80%
did he mention

00:23:15.370 --> 00:23:16.780 line:80%
any other places he had been?

00:23:19.050 --> 00:23:20.780 line:80%
Other places?

00:23:34.570 --> 00:23:35.410 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:23:35.699 --> 00:23:36.688 line:80%
what do you need with me?

00:23:36.740 --> 00:23:37.580 line:80%
How

00:23:37.740 --> 00:23:38.580 line:80%
has Zhao been lately?

00:23:39.020 --> 00:23:40.330 line:80%
Do you miss her?

00:23:41.360 --> 00:23:42.566 line:80%
Have you two made any progress?

00:23:45.940 --> 00:23:47.290 line:80%
Zhao was injured

00:23:47.290 --> 00:23:48.220 line:80%
and confined.

00:23:48.780 --> 00:23:50.333 line:80%
She writes storybooks to ease her mood.

00:23:51.050 --> 00:23:52.610 line:80%
Being able to proofread her manuscripts

00:23:52.610 --> 00:23:53.890 line:80%
is enough for me.

00:23:53.890 --> 00:23:54.940 line:80%
During this year,

00:23:55.460 --> 00:23:57.050 line:80%
you're the only one who can be with her.

00:23:57.740 --> 00:23:58.940 line:80%
And you only proofread?

00:24:00.180 --> 00:24:01.530 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:24:02.220 --> 00:24:03.850 line:80%
Your generation

00:24:03.850 --> 00:24:06.050 line:80%
has nearly been ruined

00:24:06.050 --> 00:24:06.940 line:80%
by so-called propriety.

00:24:07.660 --> 00:24:09.180 line:80%
Your father may be reckless,

00:24:09.180 --> 00:24:10.940 line:80%
but at least he has boldness.

00:24:11.740 --> 00:24:13.370 line:80%
When it's time to act, he acts.

00:24:14.500 --> 00:24:15.810 line:80%
Once her year of confinement ends,

00:24:16.500 --> 00:24:18.180 line:80%
Zhao will return to Luoying Valley.

00:24:18.700 --> 00:24:19.610 line:80%
You'll have no chance.

00:24:31.340 --> 00:24:33.780 line:80%
(Right the ways of Jianghu;
clear my name)

00:24:33.780 --> 00:24:34.700 line:80%
How is it?

00:24:35.810 --> 00:24:36.650 line:80%
Not bad.

00:24:37.020 --> 00:24:37.860 line:80%
It's done!

00:24:38.700 --> 00:24:40.020 line:80%
Hurry and tell Xingjia.

00:24:40.020 --> 00:24:41.306 line:80%
Have him inform Uncle Wordsmith

00:24:41.660 --> 00:24:42.890 line:80%
to prepare for printing.

00:24:46.660 --> 00:24:47.500 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:47.940 --> 00:24:49.020 line:80%
I have something to say.

00:24:50.050 --> 00:24:51.020 line:80%
What is it, Yuzhi?

00:24:52.610 --> 00:24:53.380 line:80%
In a few days,

00:24:53.391 --> 00:24:55.204 line:80%
my brother will marry
Miss Yang of Siqi Sect.

00:24:55.810 --> 00:24:57.220 line:80%
I must return to Guangtian Sect.

00:24:57.890 --> 00:24:59.290 line:80%
Xiaolan

00:24:59.810 --> 00:25:01.420 line:80%
is truly marrying your brother?

00:25:02.220 --> 00:25:03.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:25:05.530 --> 00:25:07.020 line:80%
do you want to go with me?

00:25:14.290 --> 00:25:16.090 line:80%
A few days ago, Han wrote to say

00:25:16.700 --> 00:25:19.290 line:80%
he's taken a liking
to knocking wooden fish

00:25:20.020 --> 00:25:21.090 line:80%
and wants to become a monk.

00:25:22.050 --> 00:25:22.940 line:80%
So?

00:25:23.220 --> 00:25:24.060 line:80%
So,

00:25:24.346 --> 00:25:25.640 line:80%
the family line of Luoying Valley

00:25:25.810 --> 00:25:27.570 line:80%
depends on me.

00:25:28.090 --> 00:25:30.220 line:80%
Yuzhi, are you willing
to marry into my family?

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:31.410 line:80%
I'm willing.

00:25:32.090 --> 00:25:33.460 line:80%
The child must take my surname.

00:25:33.980 --> 00:25:35.290 line:80%
You're willing to accept that?

00:25:35.290 --> 00:25:36.130 line:80%
I'm willing.

00:25:40.420 --> 00:25:41.330 line:80%
But I'm not.

00:25:42.610 --> 00:25:43.740 line:80%
Yuzhi, you are wonderful.

00:25:44.500 --> 00:25:46.180 line:80%
Guangtian Sect is prominent.

00:25:46.700 --> 00:25:48.290 line:80%
It's indeed a good match.

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:50.850 line:80%
But...

00:25:50.850 --> 00:25:52.660 line:80%
I'm not Mu Qingyan.

00:25:52.660 --> 00:25:54.020 line:80%
You are not Mu Qingyan,

00:25:55.220 --> 00:25:56.890 line:80%
nor need you become him.

00:25:59.090 --> 00:26:00.020 line:80%
When I was little,

00:26:00.020 --> 00:26:01.810 line:80%
there was a toy I loved dearly.

00:26:02.420 --> 00:26:04.890 line:80%
One day, I lost it by accident.

00:26:05.220 --> 00:26:07.050 line:80%
My parents bought me many toys

00:26:07.050 --> 00:26:08.780 line:80%
to cheer me up.

00:26:10.420 --> 00:26:11.420 line:80%
Some were even better

00:26:11.420 --> 00:26:13.570 line:80%
than the first one.

00:26:15.530 --> 00:26:16.850 line:80%
But I didn't want them.

00:26:19.740 --> 00:26:21.050 line:80%
Because

00:26:21.050 --> 00:26:22.850 line:80%
I couldn't love them

00:26:23.500 --> 00:26:24.980 line:80%
the way I loved the first.

00:26:28.180 --> 00:26:29.220 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:26:31.500 --> 00:26:32.370 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:26:49.740 --> 00:26:52.020 line:80%
I can't replace your first toy.

00:26:52.940 --> 00:26:53.980 line:80%
But what if one day,

00:26:54.700 --> 00:26:56.130 line:80%
you no longer long for that toy

00:26:57.980 --> 00:26:59.530 line:80%
and need a sword instead?

00:27:00.510 --> 00:27:01.370 line:80%
Yuzhi...

00:27:01.370 --> 00:27:02.420 line:80%
Zhao,

00:27:02.420 --> 00:27:03.260 line:80%
we still have time.

00:27:05.180 --> 00:27:06.020 line:80%
I can wait.

00:27:43.610 --> 00:27:44.450 line:80%
What should we do?

00:27:51.610 --> 00:27:52.450 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:27:52.940 --> 00:27:53.780 line:80%
you go.

00:27:54.090 --> 00:27:54.930 line:80%
I'll hold them off.

00:27:55.020 --> 00:27:56.286 line:80%
If we fight, we fight together.

00:27:56.370 --> 00:27:58.090 line:80%
I won't leave you alone.

00:27:58.090 --> 00:27:58.930 line:80%
Go.

00:27:58.930 --> 00:27:59.850 line:80%
Go!

00:28:00.290 --> 00:28:01.130 line:80%
I won't.

00:28:01.980 --> 00:28:03.020 line:80%
I won't!

00:28:04.290 --> 00:28:05.460 line:80%
If you die,

00:28:06.700 --> 00:28:08.370 line:80%
there is no meaning for me to live.

00:28:09.330 --> 00:28:10.850 line:80%
I want us to be together forever.

00:28:17.530 --> 00:28:18.370 line:80%
All right.

00:28:19.460 --> 00:28:21.020 line:80%
We will be together forever.

00:28:49.330 --> 00:28:50.570 line:80%
Lingbo's letter said

00:28:50.750 --> 00:28:52.343 line:80%
someone from Huangsha Gang
went missing.

00:28:52.740 --> 00:28:54.330 line:80%
She and Fengchi went to help search.

00:28:55.003 --> 00:28:55.965 line:80%
But those missing people

00:28:55.976 --> 00:28:57.500 line:80%
suddenly went mad and attacked them.

00:28:57.780 --> 00:28:58.810 line:80%
From her description,

00:28:59.570 --> 00:29:01.090 line:80%
they were surely corpse slaves.

00:29:01.090 --> 00:29:01.980 line:80%
How is Lingbo?

00:29:02.610 --> 00:29:04.220 line:80%
Fengchi protected her with his life.

00:29:04.500 --> 00:29:06.040 line:80%
They escaped only when Mr. Song Xiuzhi

00:29:06.370 --> 00:29:07.370 line:80%
arrived with men.

00:29:09.090 --> 00:29:10.020 line:80%
Master,

00:29:10.020 --> 00:29:11.740 line:80%
after Mu Qingyan became the Chief,

00:29:11.740 --> 00:29:13.290 line:80%
he forbade refining corpse slaves.

00:29:13.610 --> 00:29:14.460 line:80%
By logic,

00:29:15.420 --> 00:29:16.890 line:80%
they should not reappear.

00:29:17.850 --> 00:29:20.500 line:80%
Perhaps it's deceit.

00:29:20.890 --> 00:29:22.890 line:80%
The demonic sect has done it before.

00:29:23.780 --> 00:29:24.780 line:80%
This matter

00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:25.940 line:80%
is too strange.

00:29:26.530 --> 00:29:27.980 line:80%
I must go in person.

00:29:28.370 --> 00:29:29.210 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:30.850 line:80%
remain at Qingque Sect.

00:29:31.420 --> 00:29:32.260 line:80%
Yes.

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:11.500 line:80%
I'm out.

00:30:14.530 --> 00:30:16.610 line:80%
Congrats on completing confinement!

00:30:20.090 --> 00:30:21.050 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:30:21.420 --> 00:30:22.260 line:80%
after a year apart,

00:30:22.530 --> 00:30:23.610 line:80%
you've grown plumper.

00:30:25.180 --> 00:30:27.500 line:80%
I've labored for the sect's livelihood.

00:30:27.810 --> 00:30:29.220 line:80%
I've clearly slimmed down.

00:30:31.370 --> 00:30:33.980 line:80%
The Shanci Mushrooms
and orchids you brought back

00:30:34.460 --> 00:30:36.460 line:80%
have all been planted
in the herbal field.

00:30:37.020 --> 00:30:38.420 line:80%
I only planted them for fun.

00:30:39.130 --> 00:30:39.970 line:80%
Who knew

00:30:40.370 --> 00:30:41.500 line:80%
they would prove useful?

00:30:42.700 --> 00:30:45.660 line:80%
After three days and nights of refining,

00:30:46.130 --> 00:30:46.970 line:80%
I've finally

00:30:47.220 --> 00:30:48.890 line:80%
produced

00:30:49.330 --> 00:30:50.420 line:80%
this

00:30:50.420 --> 00:30:51.420 line:80%
Invincible

00:30:51.420 --> 00:30:52.290 line:80%
Corpse Breaker.

00:30:54.290 --> 00:30:57.090 line:80%
Xingjia, that name is truly...

00:30:58.020 --> 00:30:59.370 line:80%
Amazing.

00:30:59.370 --> 00:31:00.330 line:80%
I think so too.

00:31:02.530 --> 00:31:04.290 line:80%
Can it truly cure corpse slaves?

00:31:04.290 --> 00:31:06.020 line:80%
As long as the poison is not deep,

00:31:06.020 --> 00:31:07.420 line:80%
they'll recover at once.

00:31:07.780 --> 00:31:09.460 line:80%
Once Master finds their whereabouts,

00:31:09.810 --> 00:31:11.090 line:80%
we can save everyone.

00:31:11.420 --> 00:31:12.740 line:80%
Corpse slaves move in secrecy.

00:31:13.460 --> 00:31:14.420 line:80%
Master has no news yet.

00:31:14.980 --> 00:31:15.890 line:80%
Nie Zhe is dead.

00:31:17.180 --> 00:31:18.330 line:80%
Could these corpse slaves

00:31:18.980 --> 00:31:20.290 line:80%
be the work of the man in black?

00:31:20.660 --> 00:31:21.780 line:80%
I think

00:31:21.780 --> 00:31:22.810 line:80%
he likely knows

00:31:22.810 --> 00:31:24.980 line:80%
how to refine them.

00:31:24.980 --> 00:31:25.950 line:80%
In fact, this past year,

00:31:25.961 --> 00:31:28.227 line:80%
Master asked me to investigate
members of the Six Sects,

00:31:28.460 --> 00:31:29.420 line:80%
including Uncle Li.

00:31:31.370 --> 00:31:32.940 line:80%
But I found nothing unusual.

00:31:33.500 --> 00:31:35.780 line:80%
The man in black seems
to have vanished into thin air.

00:31:35.780 --> 00:31:38.020 line:80%
If he's behind the corpse slaves,

00:31:38.020 --> 00:31:38.860 line:80%
what does he want?

00:31:39.530 --> 00:31:40.460 line:80%
At the very least,

00:31:40.460 --> 00:31:42.850 line:80%
they wouldn't appear at Guangtian Sect
without reason.

00:31:51.890 --> 00:31:53.180 line:80%
Where's this carrier pigeon from?

00:31:53.180 --> 00:31:54.370 line:80%
I worried for Father's safety

00:31:54.370 --> 00:31:55.500 line:80%
and wrote home.

00:31:55.850 --> 00:31:56.740 line:80%
This must be the reply.

00:32:03.850 --> 00:32:04.700 line:80%
Something's wrong.

00:32:07.940 --> 00:32:09.460 line:80%
Father is in secluded cultivation.

00:32:09.460 --> 00:32:10.700 line:80%
All is well in the sect.

00:32:12.090 --> 00:32:13.220 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:32:13.220 --> 00:32:15.050 line:80%
With corpse slaves reappearing,

00:32:15.050 --> 00:32:16.130 line:80%
how can Father remain

00:32:16.130 --> 00:32:16.970 line:80%
in seclusion?

00:32:19.093 --> 00:32:20.393 line:80%
I must return to Guangtian Sect.

00:32:20.700 --> 00:32:21.700 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:32:21.700 --> 00:32:22.740 line:80%
I feel this matter

00:32:22.740 --> 00:32:24.290 line:80%
is linked to the man in black.

00:32:25.130 --> 00:32:25.980 line:80%
Perhaps

00:32:25.980 --> 00:32:28.020 line:80%
this is our chance to catch him.

00:32:28.740 --> 00:32:30.420 line:80%
My year of confinement has ended.

00:32:31.740 --> 00:32:32.940 line:80%
Let's depart at once.

00:32:32.940 --> 00:32:33.780 line:80%
All right.

00:32:43.810 --> 00:32:45.010 line:80%
Other than the snow mountains,

00:32:45.130 --> 00:32:46.050 line:80%
did he mention

00:32:46.330 --> 00:32:47.660 line:80%
any other places he had been?

00:32:47.980 --> 00:32:48.940 line:80%
Vaguely,

00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:51.780 line:80%
something about Blood...

00:32:53.570 --> 00:32:54.420 line:80%
Marsh Forest?

00:32:54.660 --> 00:32:58.820 line:80%
(Guangtian Sect, Blood Marsh Forest)

00:33:08.980 --> 00:33:09.820 line:80%
Young Master,

00:33:10.780 --> 00:33:11.700 line:80%
near Guangtian Sect,

00:33:12.020 --> 00:33:13.139 line:80%
corpse slaves have appeared.

00:33:13.740 --> 00:33:14.580 line:80%
Also,

00:33:14.740 --> 00:33:16.700 line:80%
Miss Cai has left Qingque Sect.

00:33:20.940 --> 00:33:22.333 line:80%
Her year of confinement has ended.

00:33:23.370 --> 00:33:25.220 line:80%
It's time for her to return
to Luoying Valley.

00:33:25.220 --> 00:33:26.180 line:80%
Miss Cai

00:33:26.780 --> 00:33:28.700 line:80%
went to Guangtian Sect with Song Yuzhi.

00:33:31.890 --> 00:33:33.050 line:80%
Not my business.

00:33:37.780 --> 00:33:39.460 line:80%
(Blood Marsh Forest)

00:33:39.460 --> 00:33:44.660 line:80%
(Guangtian Sect)

00:33:44.660 --> 00:33:47.580 line:80%
(Timely Chamber)

00:33:47.610 --> 00:33:48.450 line:80%
Xiuzhi.

00:33:48.780 --> 00:33:49.620 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:33:50.050 --> 00:33:50.890 line:80%
why are you back?

00:33:51.370 --> 00:33:52.210 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:33:52.500 --> 00:33:53.460 line:80%
What happened?

00:33:56.220 --> 00:33:57.060 line:80%
I must see Father.

00:33:57.270 --> 00:33:58.130 line:80%
Do not enter.

00:33:58.130 --> 00:33:59.370 line:80%
I must see him.

00:34:00.700 --> 00:34:02.500 line:80%
Xiuzhi, you are injured.

00:34:02.890 --> 00:34:04.570 line:80%
I hurt myself while practicing.

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:05.890 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:34:05.890 --> 00:34:06.810 line:80%
what is going on?

00:34:08.060 --> 00:34:09.930 line:80%
Is it related to the corpse slaves?

00:34:10.290 --> 00:34:11.130 line:80%
Master Xiuzhi.

00:34:12.740 --> 00:34:13.700 line:80%
Master Yuzhi,

00:34:13.700 --> 00:34:14.540 line:80%
you're back.

00:34:16.100 --> 00:34:16.970 line:80%
The Huangsha Gang

00:34:16.970 --> 00:34:18.700 line:80%
has summoned Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

00:34:18.700 --> 00:34:19.810 line:80%
Go take a look.

00:34:19.810 --> 00:34:20.660 line:80%
Let's go together.

00:34:22.100 --> 00:34:25.340 line:80%
(Timely Chamber)

00:34:25.580 --> 00:34:26.420 line:80%
Uncle Song,

00:34:27.140 --> 00:34:28.620 line:80%
though the Huangsha Gang is weak,

00:34:29.100 --> 00:34:30.335 line:80%
my father-in-law never bullied

00:34:30.346 --> 00:34:31.490 line:80%
the weak in decades.

00:34:32.060 --> 00:34:33.140 line:80%
As long as he had breath,

00:34:33.660 --> 00:34:35.660 line:80%
he aided those in peril.

00:34:35.660 --> 00:34:36.580 line:80%
Who would've thought

00:34:36.580 --> 00:34:38.450 line:80%
he'd die at the hands of his mates?

00:34:39.330 --> 00:34:40.890 line:80%
Senior,

00:34:40.890 --> 00:34:42.100 line:80%
please uphold justice for him.

00:34:42.410 --> 00:34:44.660 line:80%
Mr. Huang was upright.

00:34:44.930 --> 00:34:46.850 line:80%
If he suffered injustice,

00:34:46.850 --> 00:34:48.810 line:80%
we will seek justice.

00:34:48.810 --> 00:34:49.930 line:80%
Who is he?

00:34:50.450 --> 00:34:51.780 line:80%
He is Father's cousin,

00:34:52.180 --> 00:34:53.060 line:80%
my grand uncle.

00:34:53.299 --> 00:34:55.059 line:80%
He holds the highest seniority
in my family.

00:34:55.070 --> 00:34:55.910 line:80%
Lord Yang.

00:34:59.370 --> 00:35:00.850 line:80%
Why hasn't Song Shijun come?

00:35:00.850 --> 00:35:02.330 line:80%
Father is in seclusion.

00:35:02.330 --> 00:35:04.370 line:80%
I'm temporarily in charge.

00:35:04.370 --> 00:35:05.890 line:80%
Whatever you wish to say,

00:35:05.890 --> 00:35:07.100 line:80%
speak to me.

00:35:07.100 --> 00:35:07.940 line:80%
In seclusion?

00:35:09.180 --> 00:35:11.220 line:80%
Is he truly unable to come out

00:35:11.220 --> 00:35:13.330 line:80%
or too guilty to appear?

00:35:13.330 --> 00:35:14.740 line:80%
Mind your words.

00:35:14.740 --> 00:35:16.370 line:80%
What guilt does my father bear?

00:35:16.370 --> 00:35:17.330 line:80%
Very well.

00:35:17.330 --> 00:35:18.970 line:80%
Then, before everyone,

00:35:18.970 --> 00:35:20.180 line:80%
I'll speak plainly.

00:35:20.540 --> 00:35:21.450 line:80%
My father-in-law,

00:35:21.970 --> 00:35:23.580 line:80%
Leader Huang of Huangsha Gang,

00:35:24.140 --> 00:35:25.700 line:80%
retired from Jianghu years ago

00:35:26.370 --> 00:35:27.970 line:80%
and lived quietly with his family.

00:35:28.370 --> 00:35:29.700 line:80%
Yet Song Shijun

00:35:29.970 --> 00:35:32.010 line:80%
coveted the secrecy
of his mountain retreat

00:35:32.290 --> 00:35:33.890 line:80%
to refine corpse slaves.

00:35:34.330 --> 00:35:35.876 line:80%
When my father-in-law discovered this,

00:35:36.100 --> 00:35:37.890 line:80%
Song Shijun silenced them all,

00:35:38.220 --> 00:35:40.540 line:80%
slaughtering the old and young

00:35:40.540 --> 00:35:42.100 line:80%
of the gang.

00:35:44.010 --> 00:35:44.850 line:80%
Lord Yang,

00:35:45.100 --> 00:35:46.140 line:80%
words alone are not proof.

00:35:47.010 --> 00:35:47.970 line:80%
Do you have evidence?

00:35:47.970 --> 00:35:49.140 line:80%
After the massacre,

00:35:49.700 --> 00:35:51.850 line:80%
I examined the sword wounds.

00:35:52.140 --> 00:35:54.580 line:80%
All died by Guangtian sword moves.

00:35:55.290 --> 00:35:56.700 line:80%
The Six Sects are allies.

00:35:56.700 --> 00:35:58.930 line:80%
We share knowledge.

00:35:58.930 --> 00:36:00.970 line:80%
Imitating Guangtian sword marks

00:36:00.970 --> 00:36:01.810 line:80%
is not difficult.

00:36:02.140 --> 00:36:02.980 line:80%
Of course,

00:36:03.290 --> 00:36:04.580 line:80%
I wouldn't accuse lightly

00:36:04.580 --> 00:36:06.410 line:80%
based on sword moves alone.

00:36:06.780 --> 00:36:08.850 line:80%
But Song Shijun slipped once

00:36:09.100 --> 00:36:10.580 line:80%
and left a survivor.

00:36:10.890 --> 00:36:11.740 line:80%
Sha Tian'er,

00:36:18.450 --> 00:36:20.220 line:80%
show them your wound.

00:36:24.060 --> 00:36:25.140 line:80%
All know

00:36:25.410 --> 00:36:27.010 line:80%
Lord Song's sword moves are unique.

00:36:27.370 --> 00:36:28.620 line:80%
The wounds are unseen at first,

00:36:28.850 --> 00:36:29.690 line:80%
and later,

00:36:30.620 --> 00:36:31.970 line:80%
the scar blooms like a flower.

00:36:32.850 --> 00:36:34.620 line:80%
Senior, please examine it.

00:36:52.890 --> 00:36:53.730 line:80%
Indeed,

00:36:54.330 --> 00:36:57.060 line:80%
it's a wound from Shijun's sword.

00:36:57.370 --> 00:36:58.540 line:80%
What proof is that?

00:36:59.330 --> 00:37:00.540 line:80%
Everyone knows

00:37:00.540 --> 00:37:02.890 line:80%
his sword style is ornate.

00:37:02.890 --> 00:37:03.850 line:80%
Though flashy,

00:37:03.850 --> 00:37:05.100 line:80%
it's not hard

00:37:05.850 --> 00:37:06.890 line:80%
to learn.

00:37:07.180 --> 00:37:08.020 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:37:08.450 --> 00:37:09.850 line:80%
this is not your place to speak.

00:37:09.850 --> 00:37:11.060 line:80%
If we speak of fairness,

00:37:11.620 --> 00:37:12.620 line:80%
anyone may speak.

00:37:15.410 --> 00:37:16.343 line:80%
I arrived just in time.

00:37:16.660 --> 00:37:18.010 line:80%
How could I not join?

00:37:21.930 --> 00:37:22.780 line:80%
Sha Tian'er,

00:37:24.330 --> 00:37:25.180 line:80%
tell us

00:37:26.060 --> 00:37:27.490 line:80%
how Lord Song wounded you.

00:37:28.180 --> 00:37:29.410 line:80%
My master, Leader Huang,

00:37:29.850 --> 00:37:31.620 line:80%
heard villagers were disappearing.

00:37:32.220 --> 00:37:33.220 line:80%
We learned

00:37:33.540 --> 00:37:34.890 line:80%
remnants of the Nie faction

00:37:34.890 --> 00:37:36.263 line:80%
had sought refuge at Guangtian Sect

00:37:36.510 --> 00:37:37.370 line:80%
and offered

00:37:37.370 --> 00:37:39.330 line:80%
the method to refine corpse slaves

00:37:39.330 --> 00:37:40.620 line:80%
to Song Shijun.

00:37:41.220 --> 00:37:43.140 line:80%
When the secret leaked,

00:37:43.660 --> 00:37:45.060 line:80%
he slaughtered the Huangsha Gang

00:37:45.060 --> 00:37:46.740 line:80%
to conceal it.

00:37:48.700 --> 00:37:49.780 line:80%
I survived

00:37:50.220 --> 00:37:51.410 line:80%
only by feigning death.

00:37:51.700 --> 00:37:53.700 line:80%
That is only your word.

00:37:56.180 --> 00:37:57.970 line:80%
Song Shijun even hurt

00:37:57.970 --> 00:37:58.850 line:80%
his own son.

00:37:58.860 --> 00:37:59.930 line:80%
Isn't that proof?

00:38:00.450 --> 00:38:01.290 line:80%
No.

00:38:02.010 --> 00:38:02.850 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:38:02.850 --> 00:38:04.100 line:80%
what happened?

00:38:04.100 --> 00:38:05.450 line:80%
Was it truly Father?

00:38:05.450 --> 00:38:06.490 line:80%
It was not Father.

00:38:06.490 --> 00:38:08.290 line:80%
I'll answer for him.

00:38:08.290 --> 00:38:09.540 line:80%
Xiuzhi

00:38:09.540 --> 00:38:10.740 line:80%
saved Miss Qi and Mr. Dai

00:38:10.740 --> 00:38:12.620 line:80%
from corpse slaves

00:38:12.620 --> 00:38:13.470 line:80%
and uncovered

00:38:13.470 --> 00:38:15.330 line:80%
Song Shijun's plot.

00:38:15.330 --> 00:38:18.140 line:80%
Song Shijun forced Xiuzhi to hide it,

00:38:18.140 --> 00:38:19.620 line:80%
but Xiuzhi refused,

00:38:19.620 --> 00:38:22.370 line:80%
so Song Shijun tried to silence him.

00:38:22.370 --> 00:38:23.700 line:80%
I wondered why sounds

00:38:23.700 --> 00:38:25.850 line:80%
of fighting came from his chamber.

00:38:25.850 --> 00:38:26.970 line:80%
I see.

00:38:27.930 --> 00:38:29.970 line:80%
What misfortune.

00:38:30.890 --> 00:38:31.730 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:38:31.970 --> 00:38:33.490 line:80%
is this true?

00:38:36.580 --> 00:38:37.420 line:80%
Uncle Pang,

00:38:37.700 --> 00:38:38.540 line:80%
you tell us.

00:38:39.700 --> 00:38:41.060 line:80%
I don't know.

00:38:41.740 --> 00:38:42.930 line:80%
When I returned,

00:38:44.140 --> 00:38:45.450 line:80%
I saw Master Xiuzhi

00:38:45.450 --> 00:38:46.410 line:80%
fighting the Lord.

00:38:46.780 --> 00:38:47.620 line:80%
After that,

00:38:47.970 --> 00:38:49.370 line:80%
the Lord entered seclusion.

00:38:49.810 --> 00:38:50.650 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:38:51.220 --> 00:38:52.700 line:80%
Father had a momentary lapse.

00:38:52.700 --> 00:38:53.740 line:80%
Do not blame him.

00:38:58.580 --> 00:38:59.420 line:80%
Father,

00:38:59.510 --> 00:39:00.370 line:80%
why have you come out?

00:39:00.370 --> 00:39:01.220 line:80%
Father.

00:39:01.220 --> 00:39:02.330 line:80%
Song Shijun,

00:39:03.010 --> 00:39:05.180 line:80%
I want you to pay with blood!

00:39:08.440 --> 00:39:19.100 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:39:37.860 --> 00:39:42.270 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:39:42.835 --> 00:39:47.450 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:39:47.790 --> 00:39:52.355 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:39:52.880 --> 00:39:57.180 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:40:00.125 --> 00:40:04.825 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:05.350 --> 00:40:09.640 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:40:10.300 --> 00:40:14.330 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:40:14.645 --> 00:40:19.770 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:40:20.345 --> 00:40:25.155 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:25.370 --> 00:40:29.540 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:30.265 --> 00:40:34.200 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:34.700 --> 00:40:39.975 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:41:02.705 --> 00:41:07.835 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:08.200 --> 00:41:12.570 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:41:12.835 --> 00:41:16.965 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:41:17.150 --> 00:41:22.725 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪